tions**:\n  - `collectMatchSignatures()`: Fetches recent transaction signatures on match PDA (for failure diagnostics)\n  - `logRecentSignatures()`: Logs player's recent transaction signatures with slot numbers and status\n  - `formatMs()`: Human-readable duration formatting\n\n- **Error details**: `VrfTimeoutError` includes elapsed time, attempt count, last phase observed, and transaction signatures\n\n---\n\n**Summary**: These files implement a comprehensive devnet E2E test suite that validates the complete coinflip lifecycle with real Orao VRF fulfillment, dual-context player simulation, robust polling with diagnostics, and proper environment validation."}],"totalDurationMs":16270,"totalTokens":37958,"totalToolUseCount":4,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12204,"cache_read_input_tokens":24595,"output_tokens":1152,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":12204,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AeENyYJpdjuUxBr5j77amo","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are the complete contents of all four files:\n\n## 1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/on-chain.ts`\n\nThis file provides RPC-based helpers for on-chain assertions in E2E tests. Key components:\n\n- **Program IDs**: Exports `COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID` and `PLATFORM_PROGRAM_ID` derived from IDLs\n- **FEE_BPS**: Constant set to 300 (3% total platform fee)\n- **PDA Derivation**: Functions to derive:\n  - `getMatchPda(creator)` — match account PDA with seeds `[\"match\", creator]`\n  - `getConfigPda()` — coinflip config with seed `[\"coinflip_config\"]`\n  - `getPlayerProfilePda(wallet)` — player profile with seeds `[\"player_profile\", wallet]`\n- **Program Instances**: Read-only program creators (`getCoinflipProgram`, `getPlatformProgram`)\n- **Account Interfaces**: TypeScript shapes for `MatchAccount` and `PlayerProfileAccount`\n- **Fetch Helpers**: \n  - `fetchMatch()` — retrieves match PDA data, returns null if closed\n  - `fetchPlayerProfile()` — retrieves player profile, returns null if doesn't exist\n  - `getTreasuryAddress()` — reads treasury from config\n- **Balance Helpers**: `getBalanceLamports()` and `snapshotBalance()`\n- **Fee Calculation**: `calculateExpectedFee(entryAmount)` mirrors on-chain logic (fee = floor(pool × FEE_BPS / 10_000))\n- **Assertion Helpers**:\n  - `assertMatchCreated()` — validates match state after creation (waiting phase, correct tier/side, no opponent)\n  - `assertMatchClosed()` — verifies match PDA is closed\n  - `assertTreasuryFee()` — confirms treasury received expected fee delta\n  - `assertPlayerProfile()` — validates exact player stats\n  - `assertPlayerProfileDelta()` — validates stat changes since snapshot\n  - `snapshotPlayerProfile()` — captures profile stats for delta comparison (returns zeros if profile doesn't exist)\n\n---\n\n## 2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/lifecycle.spec.ts`\n\nThis is the main E2E test for the complete coinflip lifecycle. It uses two isolated browser contexts (Player A and Player B) with deterministic keypairs. The local validator has mock-VRF enabled with pre-loaded randomness.\n\n**Test Flow**:\n1. **Setup** (`beforeAll`): Fund test wallets and initialize program configs\n2. **Create**: Player A navigates to coinflip and creates a match (iron tier, heads)\n3. **On-chain verification 1**: Asserts match PDA created with correct tier/side\n4. **Join**: Player B navigates, finds the match in lobby, and joins\n5. **Snapshot**: Before resolution, capture treasury balance and both players' profile stats\n6. **Resolve & Result**: Both players wait for result (VRF pre-filled as HEADS, so Player A wins)\n7. **Claim**: Player A (winner) claims payout; match PDA is verified closed\n8. **Fee verification**: Treasury balance delta equals expected 3% fee\n9. **Profile verification**: \n   - Player A (winner): +1 game, +1 win, wagered ENTRY_AMOUNT, won payout\n   - Player B (loser): +1 game, +0 wins, wagered ENTRY_AMOUNT, won 0\n10. **Cleanup**: Player A returns to lobby; both contexts checked for console errors\n\nKey constants:\n- TIER_IRON = 0\n- SIDE_HEADS = 0\n- ENTRY_AMOUNT = 5_000_000 (0.005 SOL)\n- Timeouts: 10s–30s for various waits\n\n---\n\n## 3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n\nDeterministic wallet funding helper for reproducible local E2E tests.\n\n**Exports**:\n- **SEED_PLAYER_A**: `0xaa...aa` (32 bytes)\n- **SEED_PLAYER_B**: `0xbb...bb` (32 bytes)\n- **PLAYER_A**: Keypair derived from SEED_PLAYER_A\n- **PLAYER_B**: Keypair derived from SEED_PLAYER_B\n- **LOCAL_RPC_URL**: `\"http://127.0.0.1:8899\"`\n- **DEFAULT_AIRDROP_SOL**: 10 SOL per wallet\n\n**Functions**:\n- `fundWallet(connection, to, solAmount = 10)` — Airdrops SOL to a single wallet and confirms the transaction\n- `fundTestWallets(rpcUrl = LOCAL_RPC_URL, solAmount = DEFAULT_AIRDROP_SOL)` — Airdrops to both players, verifies balances, returns `{ playerA, playerB, connection }`. Throws if funding fails.\n\n---\n\n## 4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts`\n\nShared E2E page-object helpers for coinflip tests using CSS-class-based selectors.\n\n**Selectors** (`sel` object):\n- **Page structure**: `.coinflip-lobby`, `.coinflip-sidebar`, `.coinflip-main`\n- **Sidebar (create flow)**:\n  - `.rng-tier-selector`, `.rng-tier-btn:has(.rng-tier-gem--{tier})`, `.rng-tier-btn--selected`\n  - `.coinflip-side-selector`, `.coinflip-side-btn--heads`, `.coinflip-side-btn--tails`, `.coinflip-side-btn--selected`\n  - `.coinflip-sidebar__summary`, `.coinflip-action-btn`, `.coinflip-action-btn--secondary`\n- **Lobby (open matches)**: `.coinflip-matches__list`, `.coinflip-match-card`, `.coinflip-match-card--own`, `.coinflip-match-card--claimable`, `.coinflip-match-card__join-btn`\n- **Active match**: `.coinflip-active-match`, `.coinflip-active-match__title--won`, `.coinflip-active-match__title--lost`, `.coinflip-active-match__waiting`, `.coinflip-active-match__playing`\n- **Result & post-claim**: `.coinflip-result__outcome`, `.coinflip-result__payout`, `.coinflip-active-match__post-claim`\n- **Status**: `.coinflip-sidebar__status`, `.coinflip-sidebar__pot`, `.coinflip-error-toast`\n\n**Types**:\n- `CoinSide`: `\"heads\" | \"tails\"`\n- `Tier`: `\"iron\" | \"bronze\" | \"silver\" | \"gold\" | \"platinum\" | \"diamond\"`\n\n**Page Actions**:\n- `navigateToCoinflip(page)` — Navigate to `/coinflip` and wait for main to render\n- `selectTier(page, tier)` — Select a tier button\n- `selectSide(page, side)` — Select heads or tails\n- `createMatch(page, tier, side)` — Select tier, side, click \"Create Game\"; wait for active match view\n- `joinMatch(page, matchIndex = 0)` — Click join button on a match card; wait for active match\n- `cancelMatch(page)` — Click \"Cancel Match\" button; wait for lobby\n- `claimOrSettle(page)` — Click claim/settle button in sidebar; wait for \"Back to Lobby\"\n- `backToLobby(page)` — Click \"Back to Lobby\"; wait for lobby\n\n**Wait/Assert Primitives**:\n- `waitForPhaseLabel(page, label, timeout = 30s)` — Wait for sidebar status text (e.g., \"Waiting...\", \"Complete\")\n- `waitForResult(page, timeout = 30s)` — Returns `\"won\" | \"lost\"` based on active match title class\n- `waitForLobbyMatch(page, timeout = 15s)` — Wait for first non-claimable match card to appear\n- `assertLobbyEmpty(page, timeout = 10s)` — Assert no non-claimable match cards\n- `assertErrorToast(page, messageSubstring, timeout = 5s)` — Assert error toast visible with text\n- `assertNoErrorToast(page)` — Assert no error toasts present\n- `getSolBalance(page, walletAddress, rpcUrl)` — Fetch SOL balance via RPC\n- `trackConsoleErrors(page)` — Returns `{ errors: string[], assertClean: () => void }` to track and validate page console errors (filters favicon, fonts, third-party cookies)\n- `waitForText(page, text, timeout = 10s)` — Wait for text anywhere on page\n- `waitForLobby(page, timeout = 15s)` — Wait for lobby selector to be visible"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a9251f330e8108d4c (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 41677\ntool_uses: 4\nduration_ms: 24695</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1e7f5c42-b5f0-4a8d-9a19-a937ae16d5af","uuid":"eac07731-bdd2-4d95-aa50-9006fb56adfc","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read these files thoroughly and report their full contents:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/on-chain.ts`\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/lifecycle.spec.ts`\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n4. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts`\n\nReport the complete contents of each file.","agentId":"a9251f330e8108d4c","content":[{"type":"t